# Save old processed data

Here we save the old processed data (useful for checks against updates).

```{r}
load(
  projr::projr_path_get(
    "data-raw-public", "processed_data", "join17IncITbl.rda"
    )
)
write.csv(
  join17IncITbl,
  projr::projr_path_get(
    "output", "Vaccines-Old.csv"
  )
)
```
